      "title": "Exchange Rate Pass-Through to Domestic Producer Prices: Evidence from Korean Firm-level Pricing Survey",
      "abstract": "This note studies exchange rate pass-through to the prices of domestically produced goods, exploring the firm-level pricing survey conducted by the Bank of Korea. The data reveal the imported inputs channel of, as well as nonlinear and asymmetric, exchange rate-pass-through."
